item.description: Hey its Alex, I was wondering if anyone would be interested in climbing at the Pawtuckaway park area on Saturday, July 14th in the afternoon. I've been slacking off over the winter season and want to get back out there. If people are busy that day or if there is a better location you'd recommend, just say so. I just want to get out a bit more. There's a lot of bouldering and some top rope routes as well.
item.name: Pawtuckaway meetup
